content: Doesn't have my dept fire schedule on here and wouldn't let me customize it
Says it syncs with Google calendar but only inputs events from Google calendar to this app. Doesn't input shifts to Google calendar which is what I use. Also, does not have widget
Okay
Handy, but stopped syncing. I've checked all permissions with the phone and calendar app, and they're all good to go. Ideas?
Hard to change the schedule if it wasnt preset.
The last week of the month is not showing in the calendar. please fix or this calendar is useless.

I have loved using this app for my husband's shift pattern, it saves me having to carry a diary around with me. However just recently the last week of each month is not showing fully which is getting a bit irritating for an app I have paid for! is this likely to be sorted out soon?
Great app works well helped when we went to 48 on 72 off. Great job went pro.
Cool app, but the last week of each month is cut off and you only see a sliver of color for those days. This is on my Samsung S8+
Highlight the current day better, it's hard to make out
Horrible compared to the app I had on my iphone. Do not buy
Why is the last week of the month partially covered by the preceding one in display? If this is not fixed soon, I will be uninstalling and giving 1 star rating!
Won't sync with the note 7 sync ck does not turn green

Been using it for years. Good overall functionality, but the widget routinely gets stuck on some random day in the past and will only update if you remove the widget and replace it. Has been like this on at least my last couple of devices (Moto X, Nexus 6P).
This app didn't sync. Nothing showed up on my Google calendar... I'm probably going to ask for my money back.
The lag drives me crazy. Especially since I paid for this....
Glad to be able to support the developer. For the longest time could not purchase pro version. Also I hate ads.

My department have a very unique schedule and so far I have only found it on this app. One feature that is an  absolute must and needs to be added is the ability to export the calendar. It would definitely be rated at 5 stars if I could export it to the calendar on my MacBook.
Love this app, I'd give it 5 stars if there was a way to put my ot days on a 12 day repeat pattern!
I would give this app 5 stars if I was able to make my own labels for Groups, and if I could Widget this app
App has taken over 30 minutes to install. Not pleased with the outcome.
Great app .    If it had a widget it would be 5 stars.   (Hint hint)
Great
Would not be without it.
You can't make a custom you have to use one already  made
Would rate higher if you had the ability to print or share or send family friends and self my calendar and updates as I make them.
Great for shift schedules.
Never had an issue with this app.  Easy to setup multiple fire or EMS schedules. Google calendar sync is a great feature too. Highly recommend!
Like the color options. Wish it was more detailed where you can add events.
I had an issue setting up a 5 week custom rota. So I email for help and got a response same day then within a short time had my own custom rota done for me #105. PERFECT!!!!
Works great. Best app to keep track of schedule. Tricky to set up but works great. I would highly recommend this.
First off, support for app is outstanding. Any issues/questions can be quickly resolved. Second, once setup, works great.

Would be nice to view up to three years in advanced for long range planning. I thought the Pro version would would give me this option. Baught out to find out NOT. Could you add option to view calendars ought in the future?
Dont buy this app does not sync
don't buy this app, this is the worst app ever. you can not customize at all. waste of money and time.
So handy to have my shifts at my fingertips.  Nice to have my days off show too.  Would be nice to be able to set the pay days then put on a week repeat.
Doesnt allow you to look back on the past year. This should be addressed in one of the updates, I know that many have asked for this.
Can't make custom schedule
Worth every cent!

It's fantastic for my 4 on 4 off roster! Only suggestion is not date restricting. You can only see the current month plus 12 in advance. Also the white blank area I experience at the top of the calender - just need the margins adjusted.  Update fixed the margin issue.. unreal! Thanks!
Please add the ability to include debit days. Extra days we work in the middle of a 4 day.
Good calendar. Be even better if it had some sort of shift swapping feature included that would complete it
Had minor issue that was quickly resolved (user error). Just wish i could put my paydays on it.  Great app & support. Thanks.
Very convienent!
No annual subscription, seems perfect. Programmer fixes things instantly.
Please make full size widget that will sync with google calendars and will rate 5 stars

What I NEED is a Fire Calendar that will let me add other events to the calendar and access them easily. Notification is a MUST along with this. I have meetings on my shift as well as when I'm off duty.
I had an issue setting up my schedule and the developer personally helped me out. Kudos to Kevin!
It's the only calendar I will use for my fire shifts.
All calendar events must be done through Google calendar.... Ugh! What's the point, just use Google calendar.
Slick!!!
Its a great app but I don't understand why kelly days are marked with a + instead if just a K.  It would be great if you could see a year out also.
I like it, I do wish you could go back a month if you needed to.
Awesome app, now I can keep track of when I am scheduled to work wherever I go.
App is good, would be 5 star if it showed schedule indefinitely instead of just 12 months. Love the google calendar sync feature.
What is a debit day? Apart from that, fantastic app, works very well for UK shift system.
Great app excellent service
Works perfectly- I had a ? & they responded quickly. Great service.
Best FD calendar out there. Worth the $.
An indispensable app for UK firefighters! Even included rota days when requested from developer. Thanks!
I guess for two bucks I had hoped for a little more sync with the calendar... like events.
